__pycache__/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
/data/
models/checkpoints/
models/transformer/smoke/

# Hyperparameter sweep artifacts (models/sweeps/) are experiments, not
# production models -- only the summary leaderboard (results.json) is
# committed, so it's cheap to see what a sweep found without carrying every
# combo's checkpoints/weights/scaler in git. Production artifacts used by
# the site/bake-off still live committed under models/transformer/.
# Git won't recurse into an ignored directory to apply per-file negations,
# so directories must be explicitly re-included (the `**/` line) before the
# results.json re-include pattern can take effect -- verified with
# `git check-ignore` on both a fake artifact path and a results.json path.
/models/sweeps/**
!/models/sweeps/**/
!/models/sweeps/**/results.json
models_artifacts.zip
